  "prompt": "What is the name of the model in oyo rooms advert?",
  "response": "OYO Rooms (now commonly known as OYO) has launched numerous advertising campaigns over the years, each featuring different models, actors, and personalities based on the theme and target audience of the specific campaign. As a result, there isn't a single model associated with all OYO advertisements.\n\nIf you're referring to a particular advertisement, providing more details\u2014such as the campaign's theme, the time it was released, or any distinguishing features\u2014would help in identifying the specific model featured. Alternatively, if the model is a well-known celebrity or influencer, they might be publicly credited in the advertisement's promotional materials or on platforms like OYO's official social media channels.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, you might consider:\n\n1. **Checking the Advertisement Credits**: Sometimes, models and actors are credited in the video description if the ad is available online.\n2. **Visiting OYO's Official Channels**: OYO\u2019s official website, press releases, or social media pages might provide details about their advertising campaigns and the talent featured therein.\n3. **Contacting OYO Directly**: Reaching out to OYO\u2019s customer service or marketing department could provide specific information about the advertisement in question.\n\nIf you have a specific advertisement in mind and can provide more context or details, I\u2019d be happy to help further!",
